title: The One Where They Start the Dolphins D | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
We list the daily fantasy players to bet big on heading into Week 7 and tell you why you shouldn’t bet on Aaron Jones but should bet on the Rams. Then we provide some midrange safe bets, and Danny Heifetz makes the case for starting the Miami Dolphins defense before we build our daily fantasy lineup.
Hosts: Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck
